[{"id":"VH905640","type":"audio","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">General Speaking Directions</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\">This part requires spoken responses. Your spoken responses will be recorded. Your score will be based on what you record. It is important that you speak loudly enough and clearly so that your responses are recorded.</p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\">Cette partie exige des réponses orales. Vos réponses orales seront enregistrées. Votre note sera basée sur ce que vous aurez enregistré. Il est important que vous parliez assez fort pour que vos réponses soient enregistrées.</p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Task 3: Conversation</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\">You will participate in a conversation. Each time it is your turn to speak, you will have 20 seconds to record your response. You should participate in the conversation as fully and appropriately as possible.</p>\n\n<p class=\"direction_paragraph\" xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/apip/apipv1p0/qtiitem/imsqti_v2p2\">Vous allez participer à une conversation. Quand ce sera votre tour de parler, vous aurez 20 secondes pour enregistrer votre réponse. Vous devez participer à la conversation de façon aussi complète et appropriée que possible.</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"introduction passage-intro\">C’est une conversation avec Xavier, un camarade de classe belge. Vous participez à cette conversation parce qu’il va étudier à l’étranger et a besoin de votre aide.</p>\n\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents the outline of a conversation between Xavier and You. Xavier: Il vous salue et demande votre avis. Vous: Répondez affirmativement en donnant des détails. Xavier: Il réagit et pose une question. Vous: Répondez en donnant des détails. Xavier: Il exprime une opinion et pose encore une question. Vous: Répondez en donnant des exemples. Xavier: Il exprime son accord et demande vos conseils. Vous: Répondez en faisant des suggestions. Xavier: Il montre de l’enthousiasme et pose encore une question. Vous: Répondez et terminez la conversation.\" height=\"266\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.g02.png\" width=\"556\" /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Prompt 1</p>\n<span class=\"learnosity-feature\" data-player=\"bar\" data-src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.a01.mp3\" data-type=\"audioplayer\"></span>"},{"id":"VH905640","type":"audio","stimulusHtml":"<p>Prompt 2</p><span class=\"learnosity-feature\" data-player=\"bar\" data-src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.a02.mp3\" data-type=\"audioplayer\"></span>"},{"id":"VH905640","type":"audio","stimulusHtml":"<p>Prompt 3</p><span class=\"learnosity-feature\" data-player=\"bar\" data-src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.a03.mp3\" data-type=\"audioplayer\"></span>"},{"id":"VH905640","type":"audio","stimulusHtml":"<p>Prompt 4</p><span class=\"learnosity-feature\" data-player=\"bar\" data-src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.a04.mp3\" data-type=\"audioplayer\"></span>"},{"id":"VH905640","type":"audio","stimulusHtml":"<p>Prompt 5</p><span class=\"learnosity-feature\" data-player=\"bar\" data-src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/VH905640.a05.mp3\" data-type=\"audioplayer\"></span>"}]